---
alwaysApply: true
---

MVP (Milestones 0–1): React app in the browser at `localhost:8765`.
Vite dev proxy forwards `/api` to the FastAPI backend.

Never use localStorage or sessionStorage. Use Zustand for client-side UI state.
Never use HTML `<form>` tags — use React `onClick` and `onChange` handlers.

Milestone 3+: all Electron IPC goes through channels in `electron/preload.js`.
Never use `require()` or Node APIs directly in renderer code.
